OUT AND ABOUT
Casserly was the keynote speaker at the first Houston Texans Junior Training
Camp, held last Saturday at Memorial Park. The camp was for children ages
7-14. Participants learned the fundamentals of football through seven drill
stations manned by NFL Alumni, including former Oilers Charlie Hennigan, Ken
Houston and Don Trull.

Casserly and other members of the Texans, football operations staff also
attended league meetings in Dallas earlier in the week before returning to
Houston Thursday.

